title: Lou Dalfin  - Cavalier Faidit [mp3 320 kbps][TNTvillage]
description: The last work of Lou Dalfin, Occitan music band, after thirty years of activity relies on the collaboration of musicians such as Bunna (Africa Unite), Roy Paci, Moussu T (Massillia Sound System), Vicio (Subsonica). The sixteen tracks of Cavalier Faidit revolve around the theme of rebellion, which was developed based on the figure of the knight conscript or one of those Occitan brave soldiers who rebelled against the French invasion, which thus becomes a metaphor and a symbol for all those who today oppose the injustices.
